@page
@using System.Security.Claims
@model MedicalSuiteWeb.Pages.AboutUsModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";

    if (HttpContext.User.FindFirstValue(ClaimTypes.Role) != null)
    {
        Layout = LayoutAuthorizer.GetLayoutFromRole(this.HttpContext);
    }
    else
    {
        Layout = "_Layout";
    }
}
@{
    Layout = HttpContext.User.Identity.IsAuthenticated ? "_LayoutAuthenticated" : "_Layout";
}
<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Practice</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                <p>At our esteemed medical practice, we take pride in providing exceptional healthcare services to our community. Our team of dedicated professionals is committed to ensuring your well-being and delivering personalized care. Allow us to introduce ourselves:</p>
                <p>
                    <p><strong>Experienced Doctors:</strong>Our seasoned physicians bring years of expertise to the table. They stay abreast of the latest medical advancements and are passionate about improving lives. Whether it’s preventive care, diagnosis, or treatment, you’re in capable hands.</p>
                    <p><strong>Compassionate Nurses:</strong> Our nursing staff is the backbone of our practice. They not only administer treatments but also lend a listening ear. Their warmth and empathy create a healing environment where patients feel valued and understood.</p>
                    <p><strong>Support Staff:</strong> Behind the scenes, our efficient support staff keeps things running smoothly. From scheduling appointments to handling paperwork, they ensure a seamless experience for you. Their friendly demeanor makes every interaction pleasant.</p>
                    <p>Together, we form a cohesive unit, working harmoniously to provide the best possible treatment for each patient. Your health is our priority, and we leave no stone unturned to address your needs.</p>
                </p>
                
                <p><strong>Our Convenient Location</strong>
                    <br />
                    You’ll find us nestled in the heart of the city, strategically placed for easy access. Whether you’re a resident or a visitor, our central location ensures that quality healthcare is just around the corner. No long commutes or inconvenient detours—just a short trip to our welcoming practice.
                </p>
                
                <p> We look forward to helping you and your loved ones. Welcome to our practice! </p>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="img-container">
                <img src="https://theresiliencysolution.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/nurse-with-happy-patient.png" id="abtUsImg1" class="img-fluid" alt="Nurse being kind providing emotional support for patient">
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="img-container">
                <img src="https://www.myamericannurse.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ventilator.jpg" id="abtUsImg2" class="img-fluid" alt="Nurse being kind providing emotional support for patient">

            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="img-container">
                <img src="https://www.pewtrusts.org/-/media/post-launch-images/2020/03/aipdoctors1698x1131amrfjpgmaster/16x9_s.jpg" id="abtUsImg3" class="img-fluid" alt="Doctors using Magnetic Resoonance Imaging to view a patients tumor to determine a course of action for treatment">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide compassionate and high-quality healthcare to our patients. We strive to create a welcoming and comfortable environment where patients feel cared for and respected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <p>Our team consists of experienced and compassionate healthcare professionals who are dedicated to improving the health and well-being of our patients. We work together to provide comprehensive care and support to our patients.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Dr. John Doe - Chief Medical Officer</li>
                <li>Nurse Mary Johnson - Registered Nurse</li>
                <li>Andrea Davis - Patient Care Coordinator</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>General check-ups and physical exams</li>
                <li>Diagnostic tests and screenings</li>
                <li>Immunizations and vaccinations</li>
                <li>Chronic disease management</li>
                <li>Acute illness care</li>
                <li>Minor surgical procedures</li>
                <li>Health education and counseling</li>
                <li>Referrals to specialists</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our practice offers a comprehensive range of services to meet the healthcare needs of our patients. Whether you need a routine check-up or treatment for a specific condition, our team is here to provide you with the care you need.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

